                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220220-163-victim1526 t18220220-163-viclabel887"></join>. On the 14th of January, about five o'clock, I was in <placeName id="t18220220-163-crimeloc888">Smithfield market</placeName>
