                     <interp inst="t18220220-163-person1528" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 14th of January, I saw Ragan's cart at the door, and the prisoner leaning on it, I watched him, and saw him run off with the coat, which he took off the seat; I pursued, and saw a man take him, he threw it down.</p>
               <p>
            
